### Question 3: How would you implement merge sort on a linked list?

    ### Instructions:
    Implement MergeSort on Linked List.

    ### Code Snippet:
    <code>
    ```public Node<T> mergeSort(Node<T> head){
        // Base Case
        if(head==null||head.getNext()==null)return head;

        // Split into two halves
        Node<T> mid= getMiddle(head);
        Node<T> rightHalf=mid.getNext();
        mid.setNext(null);//break the link at the middle node

        // Recursively sort both lists
        Node<T> leftHalf=mergeSort(head);
        Node<T> rightHalfSorted=mergeSort(rightHalf);

        //Merge the two halves
        return merge(leftHalf,rightHalfSorted);
    }

    /**
	* Returns the middle node of the given linked list.
	*/
